                                                           ; 
                                                           ; See the deep dive on "Generating system data" for
                                                           ; details of the various government types

tek_:
       bss 1                                               ; The current system's tech level (0-14)
                                                           ; 
                                                           ; See the deep dive on "Generating system data" for more
